INSTALLAZIONE
1- Creare LXC Ubuntu LTS
2- Aggiungere mountpoint per disco
      # nano /etc/pve/lxc/XXX.conf
      # mp0: /mnt/hdd-data,mp=/mnt/hdd-data,ro=0
3- Installare CockPit
      # apt install --no-install-recommends cockpit -y
      # nano /etc/cockpit/disallowed-users <- disattivare root
4- Installare 45Drives Uilities
      # cd /home
      # wget https://github.com/45Drives/cockpit-file-sharing/releases/download/v4.2.10-3/cockpit-file-sharing_4.2.10-3jammy_all.deb
      # wget https://github.com/45Drives/cockpit-identities/releases/download/v0.1.12/cockpit-identities_0.1.12-1focal_all.deb
      # wget https://github.com/45Drives/cockpit-navigator/releases/download/v0.5.10/cockpit-navigator_0.5.10-1focal_all.deb
      # sudo apt install ./cockpit-*.deb
5- Installare WSDD
      # apt install wsdd -y

